    <p>The Her­itage Ta­ble: Kin X Ko­tuwa</p>
    <p>Her­itage restau­rant Kin is host­ing</p>
    <p>The Her­itage Ta­ble, fea­tur­ing cross-cul­tural col­lab­o­ra­tions with cel­e­brated chefs on a mis­sion to pre­serve her­itage. On Oct 22 and 23, chef Damian D’Silva and chef Rishi Naleen­dra from new Sri Lankan restau­rant Ko­tuwa will present a menu with myr­iad flavours.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Straits Clan Lobby, 31 Bukit Pa­soh Road MRT: Ou­tram Park</p>
    <p>WHEN: Oct 22 & 23, 6 - 10.30pm (last seat­ing: 8pm) PRICE: $168++ a per­son (Oct 22), $188++ (Oct 23, in­cludes sig­na­ture cock­tail) INFO: E-mail en­quiry@restau­rant-kin.com to make a reser­va­tion</p>


